        {
            "title": "摩根大通交易台：抄底美股正當其時 技術性洗盤可能已結束",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FxBkAsXTk0as6Ckd6GrgLw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7a74556ba514e18eb36034cb05b5f60b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 摩根大通交易部門表示，美股自8月以來最長連跌走勢為逢低買入者創造了機會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於投資者擔心人工智能概念行情的持續性以及聯儲會的貨幣政策路徑，標普500指數連續四天下跌，截至周二收盤累計下挫3.4%。摩根大通全球市場情報主管Andrew Tyler表示，這輪回調代表著股市一次「技術性洗盤」，可能調整期已經結束。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「鑒於基本面沒有任何變化，而我們的投資假設也不依賴於聯儲會放鬆政策，現在可以逢低買入，」Tyler在周三給客戶的報告中寫道。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-814781f4-9b41-37b0-9276-4ae7c1ea2460-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周三早盤美股反彈，投資者等待AI龍頭輝達收盤後公佈財報，本周四還將迎來9月非農就業數據。Tyler稱，這兩件事「可能為股市再創新高奠定基礎」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fIvgLkr9tam3.sUmHKgs3w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b839c6e35ba4391b61ce0fbcdd9fc3fc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博數據顯示，儘管標普500指數估值仍高於歷史水平，但這輪回調已將其未來12個月本益比降至21.9倍，為8月以來最低。同時，德意志銀行的一項指標顯示，上周股票倉位回落至中性水平，投資者轉為低配，表明他們短期內可能有資金重新入市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，近期一些市場人士警告稱，股市倉位過高、估值偏高可能帶來進一步回調。高盛總裁John Waldron周三表示，市場可能面臨更多損失。與此同時，Algebris Investments創始人兼執行長警告投資者應降低對全球大型科技公司的配置，其看空AI板塊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Tyler指出，市場仍有一些積極信號，例如市場廣度改善，周二約有50%的標普500成份股收盤上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當談及輝達財報和AI板塊時，Tyler表示，即使業績強勁，摩根大通也「不認為投資者會盲目追逐與AI主題相關的低質量或無盈利公司」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他說，「如果輝達財報使市場形成更集中、更理性的AI預期，那將是積極的，有助於推動指數上行，同時緩解泡沫擔憂」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題JPMorgan Trading Desk Says Selloff Offers Dip-Buying Opportunity</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%8F%B0-%E6%8A%84%E5%BA%95%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%AD%A3%E7%95%B6%E5%85%B6%E6%99%82-%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E6%80%A7%E6%B4%97%E7%9B%A4%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%B7%B2%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F-163911255.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 01:46:20",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國警告南非不要在峰會上發表二十國集團聲明",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 彭博新聞社看到的文件顯示，美國正式警告南非不要在本周末於約翰內斯堡舉行的二十國集團（G20）峰會上推動發表聯合聲明。眼下川普政府正在抵制這次G20峰會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次外交僵局尤其尷尬，因為這是非洲大陸首次主辦G20峰會，而南非總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:拉馬福薩;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/拉馬福薩\">拉馬福薩</a>將在今年年底把G20輪值主席國移交給美國。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統川普與拉馬福薩的緊張關係在5月白宮橢圓形辦公室會晤時達到頂峰，當時拉馬福薩在鏡頭前遭到川普的嚴厲斥責。隨後川普宣布不會出席峰會，並最終全面抵制此次峰會。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3d0255c3-d2a6-360c-af03-00458f12f5e6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國公開反對南非擔任G20輪值主席國及其以團結、平等和可持續性為核心的議程，這是拉馬福薩推動建立更包容的全球秩序的一部分。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「華盛頓的缺席削弱了它在G20成果中的作用，」南非外交部發言人Chrispin Phiri周三通過電話表示。「我們不能允許‘以缺席相逼’成為可行的手段。這會導致機制癱瘓和集體行動的瓦解。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Warns South Africa Not to Issue G-20 Statement at Summit</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Antony Sguazzin、Mario Parker、Rivaldo Jantjies、Daniel Carvalho.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%A8%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8A%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E4%BA%8C%E5%8D%81%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-144840840.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 00:25:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "姍姍來遲的美國8月貿易數據顯示逆差收窄 進口下降",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國官方數據周三顯示，8月份美國貿易逆差有所收窄，進口錄得四個月來最大降幅。此前，由於政府停擺導致數據發布延遲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國商務部稱，當月商品和服務貿易逆差較前月收窄近24%，至596億美元。此前彭博對經濟學家調查得出的預估中值為逆差604億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該貿易報告原定10月7日發布，但因聯邦政府史上最長停擺而推遲。原定11月4日發布的9月貿易數據更新發布時間尚未公佈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">8月進口下降5.1%，出口小幅上升。上述數據未經通膨調整。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7f3596c6-cfd3-318a-b1e2-64312d63aefb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Trade Deficit Narrowed in August as Imports Declined</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Chris Middleton.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A7%8D%E5%A7%8D%E4%BE%86%E9%81%B2%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B8%E6%9C%88%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E9%80%86%E5%B7%AE%E6%94%B6%E7%AA%84-%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D-140228936.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-19 22:41:03",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本財務大臣與央行行長重申共同協議 旨在克服通縮、實現可持續成長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/coO7gRWBlwOthLeo5pI66w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e03ab191ea42868d2d62ffcf68f1eb07\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本財務大臣片山皋月表示，她已向日本央行行長植田和男及成長戰略大臣城內實確認了監測市場走勢的必要性，官員們重申了旨在克服通貨緊縮並實現可持續成長的共同協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們確認，三人將竭儘全力管理政策，以實現穩定的通膨和可持續的經濟成長，」片山在周三三位官員會晤後對記者表示。「我們還重申，將以高度緊迫感監測市場動態，並與市場保持密切溝通。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lOU4zCZGvZQosr7E30hQ4w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/252594403d912550c2c7d41aaac5c9dd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">片山皋月表示，她與植田和男並未特別討論匯率問題。她表示，植田和男按照現有立場闡述了日本央行的政策。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d49cc67c-d938-349f-991b-e125e17453a4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「根據我聽到的內容，我對他的表態沒有任何的異議，」片山補充道，表明她總體上認同央行的政策方向。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此番言論推動日圓兌美元匯率突破1美元兌156關口，創下1月以來的最弱。此前在片山開始發言時，約在155.65位置。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2013年制定的聯合聲明闡明了政府與央行共同致力於終結通縮、促進可持續經濟成長的決心，同時將央行的物價穩定目標設定為2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">片山表示，雙方同意對現有聲明進行小幅度的技術性修訂，將相關政府機構名稱改為「日本成長戰略總部」，但協議核心內容保持不變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Finance Minister Reaffirms Joint Accord With BOJ’s Ueda</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%B2%A1%E5%8B%99%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E8%88%87%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E6%97%A8%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%8B%E6%9C%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%B8%AE-%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-113108122.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-19 20:05:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國抵押貸款活動減少 借貸成本小幅上升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"811\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vtSz9b5HJhmxBL08hLprdw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgxMTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ccae7ad5a4f4a64cd9272640492a49ad\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 上周美國<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:抵押貸款;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/抵押貸款\">抵押貸款</a>活動下滑，因住房融資成本持續攀升，進一步印證了房地產市場舉步維艱的現狀。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">抵押貸款銀行家協會(MBA)的指標顯示，截至11月14日當周，購房或再融資貸款申請綜合指數下降5.2%。周三公佈的數據顯示，30年期抵押貸款合約利率微升3個基點，至6.37%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該協會再融資指標下滑7.3%，至兩個月低點，而購房申請指數則下降2.3%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"811\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5Id_yYihixZp_r.CimcPcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgxMTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1fdfa5d2723043fa7ff8717cb559cc7d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">抵押貸款活動放緩進一步印證了住房市場持續面臨逆風，包括購房負擔能力不足。為刺激購房需求，開發商正通過降價和優惠措施吸引買家。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4294def5-97cc-300c-904c-de78514bb735-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而，全美住宅建築商協會與富國銀行周二發布的數據顯示，本月銷售預期有所下滑，且更多建築商認為市場狀況不佳。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國住宅建築商信心略有回升 促銷激勵難以打動謹慎買家</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">MBA調查自1990年以來每周進行一次，調查數據來自抵押貸款銀行家、商業銀行和儲蓄機構。該數據涵蓋了美國75%以上的零售住宅抵押貸款申請。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Mortgage Activity Declines as Borrowing Costs Edge Higher</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%BC%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91-%E5%80%9F%E8%B2%B8%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-130610049.html",
